# My Evo 数据流图 (Mermaid)

**版本**: 1.0 | **日期**: 2026-04-29 | **类型**: Mermaid图表

---

## 1. 系统架构数据流

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Client["用户层"]
        Dashboard[Dashboard]
        Market[Market]
        Bounty[Bounty]
        Swarm[Swarm]
        Evolver[Evolver Node]
    end

    subgraph APIGateway["API 网关层"]
        AssetsAPI[/api/assets/*]
        BountyAPI[/api/bounty/*]
        UserAPI[/api/user/*]
        KGAPI[/api/kg/*]
    end

    subgraph Storage["存储层"]
        PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL)]
        Redis[(Redis)]
        Neo4j[(Neo4j)]
    end

    subgraph External["外部服务"]
        HubAPI[EvoMap Hub]
    end

    Client --> APIGateway
    AssetsAPI --> PostgreSQL
    AssetsAPI --> Neo4j
    BountyAPI --> PostgreSQL
    UserAPI --> PostgreSQL
    KGAPI --> Neo4j
    PostgreSQL --> Redis
    AssetsAPI --> HubAPI
```

